<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Invitation Successfully Sent</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f5f5f5;
        }

        .email-container {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            margin: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6B46C1 0%, #9333EA 100%);
            padding: 30px 40px;
            text-align: center;
            color: white;
        }

        .logo {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .logo-icon {
            width: 32px;
            height: 32px;
            background-color: white;
            border-radius: 6px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            margin-right: 10px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #6B46C1;
            font-size: 18px;
        }

        .logo-text {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        .header-title {
            font-size: 22px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin: 0;
        }

        .success-badge {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.2);
            color: #F0FDF4;
            padding: 8px 16px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 14px;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }

        .content {
            padding: 40px;
        }

        .greeting {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #374151;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .main-message {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #374151;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .service-card {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ECFDF5 0%, #F0FDF4 100%);
            border: 2px solid #BBF7D0;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 24px;
            margin: 25px 0;
            position: relative;
        }

        .service-card::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            height: 4px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #22C55E 0%, #16A34A 100%);
            border-radius: 12px 12px 0 0;
        }

        .service-title {
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #1F2937;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .service-detail {
            display: flex;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            font-size: 15px;
        }

        .service-label {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #6B7280;
            min-width: 120px;
        }

        .service-value {
            color: #374151;
        }

        .subject-badge {
            display: inline-block;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6B46C1 0%, #9333EA 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 6px 12px;
            border-radius: 16px;
            font-size: 13px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .status-section {
            background-color: #F0F9FF;
            border: 1px solid #0EA5E9;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 25px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .status-icon {
            font-size: 32px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .status-title {
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #0369A1;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }

        .status-text {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #0284C7;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        .tracking-section {
            background-color: #F8FAFC;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 24px;
            margin: 25px 0;
        }

        .tracking-title {
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #1F2937;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .tracking-steps {
            display: grid;
            gap: 16px;
        }

        .tracking-step {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 12px;
            background-color: white;
            border-radius: 6px;
            border: 1px solid #E5E7EB;
        }

        .step-number {
            width: 28px;
            height: 28px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6B46C1 0%, #9333EA 100%);
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            color: white;
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-right: 12px;
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }

        .step-text {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #374151;
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        .next-steps {
            margin: 25px 0;
        }

        .next-steps h3 {
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #1F2937;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
        }

        .steps-list {
            margin: 0;
            padding-left: 20px;
        }

        .steps-list li {
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            color: #374151;
            font-size: 15px;
        }

        .cta-section {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 30px 0;
        }

        .cta-button {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6B46C1 0%, #9333EA 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
            display: inline-block;
            font-size: 15px;
            margin: 0 8px 8px 0;
        }

        .cta-button.secondary {
            background: white;
            color: #6B46C1;
            border: 2px solid #6B46C1;
        }

        .footer {
            background-color: #F9FAFB;
            padding: 24px 40px;
            text-align: center;
            border-top: 1px solid #E5E7EB;
        }

        .footer-text {
            color: #6B7280;
            font-size: 14px;
            margin: 5px 0;
        }

        .footer-links {
            margin-top: 15px;
        }

        .footer-link {
            color: #6B46C1;
            text-decoration: none;
            margin: 0 10px;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        .copyright {
            margin-top: 15px;
            color: #9CA3AF;
            font-size: 13px;
        }

        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .email-container {
                margin: 10px;
            }

            .header,
            .content,
            .footer {
                padding: 20px;
            }

            .service-card,
            .tracking-section,
            .status-section {
                padding: 16px;
            }

            .cta-button {
                display: block;
                margin: 8px 0;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="email-container">
        <div class="header">
            <div class="logo">
                <div class="logo-icon">G</div>
                <div class="logo-text">GradPal</div>
            </div>
            <h1 class="header-title">Invitation Successfully Sent</h1>
            <div class="success-badge">âœ… Delivered</div>
        </div>

        <div class="content">
            <div class="greeting">
                Hello {{teacherName}},
            </div>

            <div class="main-message">
                Great news! Your service invitation has been successfully sent to the selected student. The invitation
                is now in their inbox and they'll be able to review the details and decide whether to join your
                autonomous learning service.
            </div>

            <div class="service-card">
                <div class="service-title">{{serviceTitle}}</div>

                <div class="service-detail">
                    <div class="service-label">Teacher:</div>
                    <div class="service-value">{{teacherName}}</div>
                </div>

                <div class="service-detail">
                    <div class="service-label">Subject:</div>
                    <div class="service-value">
                        <span class="subject-badge">{{subject}}</span>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="service-detail">
                    <div class="service-label">Status:</div>
                    <div class="service-value">Invitation Sent</div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="status-section">
                <div class="status-icon">ðŸ“¤</div>
                <div class="status-title">Invitation Delivered Successfully</div>
                <div class="status-text">
                    The student has received your invitation and can now review the service details. They'll be notified
                    via email and can access the invitation through their GradPal dashboard.
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="tracking-section">
                <div class="tracking-title">What happens next:</div>
                <div class="tracking-steps">
                    <div class="tracking-step">
                        <div class="step-number">1</div>
                        <div class="step-text">Student receives and reviews the invitation</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="tracking-step">
                        <div class="step-number">2</div>
                        <div class="step-text">Student decides to accept or decline the invitation</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="tracking-step">
                        <div class="step-number">3</div>
                        <div class="step-text">You'll receive a notification of their decision</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="tracking-step">
                        <div class="step-number">4</div>
                        <div class="step-text">If accepted, the service begins automatically</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="next-steps">
                <h3>While you wait:</h3>
                <ul class="steps-list">
                    <li>Monitor your dashboard for invitation responses</li>
                    <li>Prepare any additional materials for when students join</li>
                    <li>Check your notification settings to stay updated</li>
                    <li>Send additional invitations if you have more capacity</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="main-message">
                <strong>Invitation Timeline:</strong> Students typically respond within 24-48 hours. If they haven't
                responded within a week, you may want to follow up directly or send a reminder through the platform.
            </div>

            <div class="cta-section">
                <a href="#" class="cta-button">View Dashboard</a>
                <a href="#" class="cta-button secondary">Send More Invitations</a>
            </div>

            <div class="main-message">
                <strong>Need assistance?</strong><br>
                Our support team is here to help with invitation management, student communication, or any questions
                about your autonomous service setup.
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <div class="footer-text">Thank you for creating engaging learning experiences with GradPal.</div>
            <div class="footer-links">
                <a href="#" class="footer-link">www.gradpal.io</a>
                <a href="#" class="footer-link">support@gradpal.io</a>
            </div>
            <div class="copyright">Â© 2025 GradPal. All rights reserved.</div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>